The paper focuses on optimizing the energy consumption and latency in heterogeneous cellular networks (HetNets) by jointly optimizing cloud selection, transmit power, receive beamformer, and transmit covariance matrix. This involves aspects of network infrastructure (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), distributed computing (cs.DC), systems and control (cs.SY), and architecture (cs.AR). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
